msgid ""
"*Optional*: If Traffic Server will be operating strictly as a forward "
"proxy, you will want to disable reverse proxy support by modifying "
":ts:cv:`proxy.config.reverse_proxy.enabled` in :file:`records.config`::"
msgstr ""

